{"tid":429726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子街頭力抗持竹3匪","createTime":"2017-10-09T07:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T07:35:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76a244661411c5f00bd22250092c9a9be359e678","tid":429726,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176776&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176776%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=5fb7e2c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176776%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&h=23850982\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176776&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009</a><br />\n<br />\n男子街頭力抗持竹3匪<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角鬧市昨晨發生街頭搶劫事件！一名男子偕妻女在一間餐廳食完早餐，步出門外之際，3名匪徒竟在街頭手持竹枝，追打男事主及拳打腳踢，企圖搶去他的背囊，男事主奮力抗賊力保不失，賊人見事敗不敢糾纏拔足狂奔，事主頭手受傷送院敷治，警員在場兜截匪徒未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/09la6p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F09la6p4.jpg&h=305301a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奮力抗賊男事主額頭、眼角及手受傷，送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趁離開餐廳圖搶背囊<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨清晨6時許，姓潘（59歲）男子偕妻子及女兒，到旺角砵蘭街244號一間餐廳食早餐，結賬離開甫步出餐廳門口，突有3名中國籍男子撲出，分別手持竹枝追打襲擊及拳毆潘，企圖搶去他的背囊，潘以一敵三，奮力抗賊，4人拉扯糾纏，3匪見不得逞，向亞皆老街方向逃去。潘的背囊幸保不失，但被毆致額頭、眼角及手受傷，他負傷報警求助，由女兒陪同送院。據悉，背囊內並非存有巨款，警方不排除匪徒「打盲毛」犯案，正追緝3匪歸案。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭文輝、潘志能"}]}